        "messages": {
          "values": [
            {
              "content": "=You are writing a short, professional payment reminder email on behalf of \"Turbo Tech\" — a small business reaching out to a client about a pending payment.\n\nClient details:\n- Name: {{ $('Filter').item.json[\"Client Name\"] }}\n- Service/Item: {{ $('Filter').item.json[\"Service/Item\"] }}\n- Amount Due: {{ $('Filter').item.json.Amount }}\n- Due Date: {{ $('Filter').item.json[\"Due Date\"] }}\n\nWrite a friendly but professional email reminding them about this payment. Keep it short (3-4 sentences), polite, and include their name and the amount/due date naturally in the message. Do not include a subject line — just the email body. Sign off as \"Turbo Tech\". If the deadline is passed, be a little harsh."
            }
